        <div class="relative space-y-8 py-12 p-8">
          <script src="https://cdn.lordicon.com/lordicon.js"></script>
          <lord-icon
              src="https://cdn.lordicon.com/abwrkdvl.json"
              trigger="loop"
              state="loop-all"
              colors="primary:#121331,secondary:#7692ff"
              style="width:100px;height:100px">
          </lord-icon>

          <div class="space-y-2">
            <h5
              class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-white transition group-hover:text-secondary"
            >
              Our Purpose
            </h5>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-justify">
              Our purpose is to become the go-to destination for mobile phone enthusiasts and professionals alike. We aim to achieve this by:
              <br/>
              <br/>

              <li>Offering a comprehensive range of mobile phones and accessories from leading brands</li><br/>
              <li>Providing exceptional customer service to build trust and loyalty among our customers</li><br/>
              <li>Continuously improving our online shopping experience to meet and exceed customer expectations</li><br/>

