          </lord-icon>

          <div class="space-y-2">
            <h5
              class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-white transition group-hover:text-secondary"
            >
              Future Vision
            </h5>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-justify">
              In the future, we envision Parscomtel as a thriving online platform that not only meets but exceeds the expectations of our customers. We plan to achieve this by:
              <br/>
              <br/>
              <li>Expanding our product offerings to include even more mobile phone models and accessories</li>
              <li>Enhancing our customer service by introducing new communication channels and support options</li>
              <li>Implementing innovative technologies to improve the overall shopping experience and stay ahead of the competition</li>

