              trigger="loop"
              colors="primary:#121331,secondary:#7692ff"
              style="width:100px;height:100px">
          </lord-icon>

          <div class="space-y-2">
            <h5
              class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-white transition group-hover:text-secondary"
            >
              Conclusion
            </h5>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-justify">
              At Parscomtel, we are committed to providing our customers with the best possible shopping experience. By offering a wide variety of brands, outstanding customer service, and fast, secure delivery, we strive to become the preferred online destination for mobile phone and accessory enthusiasts. Our purpose and future vision drive us to continuously improve and grow, ensuring that we remain a trusted and reliable source for our valued customers.
